node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Daily Facts on July 22, 2021. May be an image of food and text that says 'DailyFacts For April Fools Day in 1998, Burger King took out a full-page ad in USA Today introducing a Whopper designed especially for lefties. The new burger would contain the same ingredients as the original, but rotated 180°. Thousands of customers swarmed BK restaurants requesting the "lefty" Whopper.'.

node.text:
Like History? Check out our 2nd page @history_in_images
Source:
